[Amit Varma]: know, 1817 to 1920 and the three pandemics that shaped our nation profoundly during that

01:06:24.600 --> 01:06:28.280
[Amit Varma]: period and yet we don't remember them as we should and they hold a lot of lessons for

01:06:28.280 --> 01:06:29.320
[Amit Varma]: the present day.

